WRITING: Writing skillfully and persuasively

Category: Creative
Base skill: 25% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

Writing well enough to inform, entertain, or persuade: reports,
correspondence, stories, propaganda. Distinct from Literacy (the
basic ability to read and write a language) - this is skill at the
craft itself.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

SEE ALSO: skills, art, forgery
